(## 1\) What AnchorOS is designed to do) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- AnchorOS is a modular governance layer for ChatGPT sessions.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- It externalizes durable session behavior into capsules so new sessions can bootstrap into) Tj
0 -14 Td
(a stable, governed state.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Core architecture revolves around Manifest \(authority\), Bootstrap \(loader\), Spec \(rules\),) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Protocol \(operations\), and Index \(mapping\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
